text: Assem Mussarova (born 13 August 1990) is a Kazakhstani female water polo player. She competed for the Kazakhstan women's national water polo team in the 2013 World Aquatics Championships, 2015 World Aquatics Championships, and 2017 World Aquatics Championships. == References == ==Other websites== *Assem+Mussarovazimbio * mussarova-assem-fights-with-webster depositphotos Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani water polo players
